label: A10B2C_hP39_172_5c_c_a-001
title: Sr[S$_{2}$O$_{6}$][H$_{2}$O]$_{4}$ Structure
comments:
This structure is the enantiomorph of the \href{current_web_home_dir/A10B2C_hP39_171_5c_c_a-001}{Sr[S$_{2}$O$_{6}$][H$_{2}$O]$_{4}$ (A10B2C\_hP39\_171\_5c\_c\_a) structure}. Only the non-hydrogen atoms are included in the prototype. 
 Space group $P6_{4}$ \#172 allows an arbitary choice for the origin of the $z$-axis.  We set this by taking $z_{1} = 0$ for the Sr site. 
 The ICSD entry is for space group $P6_{2}$ \#171.
